#

Kung Pao Chicken

25 min
$12
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinNut-Free Option

Cuisine:

Chinese

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickEasyStir-Fry

Description

A spicy, savory, and slightly sweet stir-fry featuring tender chicken, crunchy peanuts, and vibrant vegetables.

Ingredients

  • boneless, skinless chicken breasts: 1 lb
  • soy sauce: 3 tbsp
  • cornstarch: 1 tbsp
  • vegetable oil: 2 tbsp
  • red bell pepper: 1, diced
  • green bell pepper: 1, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • ginger: 1 inch, minced
  • dried red chilies: 5-8
  • roasted peanuts: 1/2 cup
  • scallions: 2, sliced
  • rice or noodles: to serve
